summary: This code specifies the required libraries for the "metalazero/native/lazero_win10_amd64" project. The developer notes that using "ptyprocess" is not recommended on Windows due to lack of support, and lists alternative libraries such as "pyte", "tornado", "twisted", "requests", and "service_identity".
